name: Brompton Canadian Cash Flow Kings ETF
longDescription: The fund performance of mid-to large capitalization Canadian equities whose issuers exhibit high free cash flow relative to their enterprise value. The Index uses a rules-based methodology to gain exposure to shares of 35 TSX-listed companies with the highest free cash flow yields. Brompton Canadian Cash Flow Kings ETF (KNGC) is designed to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Brompton Index One Canadian Cash Flow Kings Index.
